snippet.title: International Snooker Official Trailer by Big Head Games
snippet.description:
"Quite possibly the most realistic Snooker game to come to any gaming platform, working closely with Michaela Tabb the world's most famous Snooker and Pool referee Big Head Games have crafted the ultimate cue sports simulation, with easy to pickup and play controls and months of gameplay as you fight through a pro player's career."

We uploaded this trailer with permission from the developer. If this game interests you, be sure to help support the developer at one of the links below.

GamesGate: http://www.gamersgate.com/DD-ISNOOKER/international-snooker
Green Man Gaming: http://www.greenmangaming.com/s/us/en/pc/games/sports/international-snooker/
Shiny Loot: http://www.shinyloot.com/international-snooker
